The mechanism for the transformation procedure of SnSe to Se NR is schematically shown in Fig. 1. The reaction between ball-milled SnSe particles and oxalic acid in aqueous solution is triggered under hydrothermal condition, leading to the formation of a complex intermediate, as represented in equation (1).1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
